default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultFunding of a flagship project in Israel/Palestine th
defaultat is focused on empowering young people in order to achieve peace. 
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultCreation of a parallel fund directed at youth empowerment, including economic investment and job creation projects
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHighlighting of this sort of work by ambassadors, diplomats and FCO staf
defaultf so as to promote those working in this area, and foster a sense of optimism 
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDonation of Embassy facilities to projects that seek to foster conflict resolution, creating a “safe space” within which people can meet. 
default-
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMeeting with such groups whenever Mini
defaultsterial/Parliamentary visits take place.
